definitions.definition: Of clothing or part of a garment , containing a strip or strips of elastic , especially in the waistband , cuffs or the ends of the legs , in order to make the clothing fit snugly .

main_definition: Of clothing or part of a garment , containing a strip or strips of elastic , especially in the waistband , cuffs or the ends of the legs , in order to make the clothing fit snugly .
